          <title>
            <string language="en">George Washington Appoints First Marshals, 1789</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">George Washington Ernennt Erste Marschälle, 1789</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">George Washington Nomme Les Premiers 
Maréchaux, 1789</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">George Washington Aponta Os Primeiros Marshals, 
1789</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">George Washington Nomina I Primi Marshals, 1789</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Θ*Γεοργε Ουάσιγκτον διορίζει πρώτο Marshals, 1789</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">George Washington Designa A Primeros Mariscales, 
1789</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">tells the history of the U.S. Marshal service and explains how the Marshals' role in law enforcement has evolved over time.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">erklärt die Geschichte des VEREINIGTE STAATEN 
Marschallservices und erklärt, wie die Rolle der Marschälle in der 
Gesetzdurchführung über Zeit entwickelt hat.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">dit l'histoire du service de maréchal des 
ETATS-UNIS et explique comment le rôle des maréchaux dans 
l'application de loi a évolué avec le temps.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">diz o history do serviço do marshal de ESTADOS 
UNIDOS e explica como o papel dos marshals' no enforcement de lei 
evoluiu sobre o tempo.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">dice alla storia del servizio del marshal degli 
STATI UNITI e spiega come il ruolo dei marshals nell'applicazione di 
legge si è evoluto col tempo.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">λέει την ιστορία της ΑΜΕΡΙΚΑΝΙΚΗΣ Marshal υπηρεσίας 
και εξηγεί πώς ο ρόλος του Marshals στην επιβολή νόμου έχει 
εξελιχθεί κατά τη διάρκεια του χρόνου.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">dice la historia del servicio del mariscal de 
ESTADOS UNIDOS y explica cómo el papel de los mariscales en la 
aplicación de ley se ha desarrollado en un cierto plazo.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
